# Specs to skip during e2e generation.
# One path per line (relative to specs root). Lines starting with # are comments.

# ============================================================
# ARM RESOURCE MANAGER SPECS — Triage (task 20.13, 2026-03-08)
# ============================================================
# All 9 ARM specs emit TypeSpec→C# successfully (task 20.7 added management=true).
# Tasks 20.8–20.12e fixed many ARM compilation errors (AzureLocation namespace,
# ambiguous references, namespace collisions, infrastructure API issues, flavor-
# aware protocol methods). However, 2,358 CS errors remain across 9 specs due
# to deep ARM infrastructure gaps that require further emitter work.
#
# Major error categories (by count):
#   - CS0122 (732): ProtocolOperationHelpers, OperationFinalStateVia inaccessible
#   - CS0117 (404): Missing members — Widget.FromResponse, etc.
#   - CS1503 (328): Type conversions — Guid→string, wrong argument types
#   - CS1061 (188): Missing methods on generated types
#   - CS0246 (148): Missing type/namespace references
#   - CS0029/CS0030 (244): Implicit/explicit conversion errors
#   - CS0103 (120): Names not in current context
#   - CS1729 (72): Wrong constructor argument counts (OptionalBody, etc.)
#   - CS0128 (40): Duplicate local variable definitions
#   - CS1744 (36): Named argument conflicts (cancellationToken)
#   - CS7036 (28): Missing required parameters
#   - CS0118 (14): NonResource namespace/type collision (non-resource spec)
#   - CS0144 (4): Cannot create abstract class instances
#
# These errors reflect missing ARM-specific infrastructure:
#   - Resource operation patterns (CRUD, LRO, collections)
#   - FromResponse/ToRequestContent model serialization hooks
#   - ARM-flavored OptionalBody, ProtocolOperationHelpers
#   - Proper Guid→string path parameter handling
#
azure/resource-manager/common-properties
azure/resource-manager/large-header
azure/resource-manager/method-subscription-id
azure/resource-manager/multi-service
azure/resource-manager/multi-service-older-versions
azure/resource-manager/multi-service-shared-models
azure/resource-manager/non-resource
azure/resource-manager/operation-templates
azure/resource-manager/resources

